akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602030/extras/stylized.png?t=1738840952\" /><br><br>Beautifully crafted alien landscapes meet colorful bomb bursts and delicious chain reactions. Find the sights and sounds of an entire carnival arcade within one 20-minute level!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602030/extras/World_2.gif?t=1738840952\" /><br><br><br><br>Entropy Survivors is a prequel set in the Shoulders of Giants universe\u2013but don\u2019t worry: this game stands completely on its own.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Cactus Expanse","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602030/529fe203151123e07f94f8f0b1d1e3deca686e31.jpg"},{"name":"Timber Falls","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602030/326a101bb686d37b66c08257d1f85c0907cb6cbb.jpg"},{"name":"Amethyst Alley","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602030/9970828c791b13a5a017120256cfd503d4e9f8ca.jpg"},{"name":"Hall of Flame","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602030/66927ad4340cb94b6fe31ce43a3eb120bab28473.jpg"},{"name":"Princess Kisses","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602030/296f86afa36bfe7ac8de03561878e991b80c700e.jpg"},{"name":"Lose Your Tail","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602030/2667f5fcf8ffd45020b7f30a67e78e46d39fb729.jpg"},{"name":"Not Easy (Being Green)","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602030/3ae8b2ed0003015318260fec2594723b28e00b32.jpg"},{"name":"Warts and All","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602030/be620295816c66d05820b8f70938423be774eb33.jpg"},{"name":"Prepare to Croak","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602030/693ad24c